## Pages Using This Pattern

- **Portrait (default):** catholicate, holy-synod, saints, the-church, administration, training, publications, lectionary, institutions, theological-seminaries, ecumenical, downloads-old
- **Landscape:** directory (`frame="landscape"`)

When adding a new hub grid under `src/app/mosc-redesign/(syro)/`, **import and use `MoscHubCardMedia`** ‚Äî do not hand-roll `Image` + fixed aspect boxes.

